        "description": "Delivery of the Home Upgrade Grant (HUG2) programme. (\u00a341m secured by Cosy Homes in Lancashire - CHilL - for the whole of Lancashire. Jurisdiction share expected to be around \u00a33million). https://www.chil.uk.com/home-upgrade-grant The scheme aims to raise the energy efficiency of low energy performance homes that do not have gas central heating by installing insulation measures, renewable technologies such as heat pumps and solar PV and upgrading windows from single to double glazed. The scheme is open to low-income households and properties within specified postcodes. It is expected that 100 properties will be improved this financial year.",
