        "financeStatus": "Other impact indicator(s): Other - Modal shift from private vehicles and taxis to bikeshare (estimated based on data taken from 7191 journey end surveys completed by users in the city between 01 June 2023 and 01 July 2024): 23,380 journeys (71,017 km)",
