        "renewableTarget": "The Essex Climate Action Commission (ECAC) produced the 'Net Zero: Making Essex Carbon Neutral' report, which provides recommendations for climate actions structured around six core themes. The report explores each theme highlighting climate related risks, impacts, and scenarios. (https://www.essexclimate.org.uk/sites/default/files/DS21_7178%20ECAC_Commission_Report-Final.pdf ) The ECAC commissioned a study to investigate the impact of its recommendations for climate actions, including a baseline of emissions in Essex and a future emissions pathway. (https://www.essex.gov.uk/sites/default/files/migration_data/files/assets.ctfassets.net/knkzaf64jx5x/rzuw1LpExzIc9v4dUjk03/dcb7427bf2569c3a75134addc2d27dd2/Climate-Action-Baseline-and-Pathway-to-Net-Zero.pdf ) This study is supplemented by the work performed for Essex County Council by Element Energy in 2020 in producing Essex Future Energy Scenarios and Pathways to Net Zero. \\n",
