        "description": "Identify and utilise Vacant and Derelict Land (VDL) for the improvement of green infrastructure, restoration of public realm and open space, creation of community growing spaces, and enhancement of woodland habitat and biodiversity. Two projects have received a total of \u00a32,633,641 from the VDL Investment Programme funding by the Scottish Government, covering the 2025/26 financial year. The Scottish Government has also confirmed allocation \u00a31.908 million to the VDL fund for 2025/26. Ten projects have been awarded funding from this allocation (https://onlineservices.glasgow.gov.uk/councillorsandcommittees/submissiondocuments.asp?submissionid=119263).",
