        "description": "A focus on sustainable procurement has led to replacing our cleaning products in Leisure services buildings with alternative sustainable products. This has reduced the amounts of products procured, cut delivery costs and removed the requirement for COSHH training. The new alternative, sustainable products are now being introduced across all council buildings. Replaced our workwear with sustainable alternatives across Groundwork services. These include clothing made from recycled and sustainable materials. We have also replaced our petrol-powered handheld gardening equipment with battery powered replacements. We regularly review new technology and invite suppliers in to showcase their new products. \\n",
