        "description": "The North East Combined Authority recently announced the launch of the Carbon and Nature Marketplace, designed to attract private funding for local low carbon projects. NTC undertook feasibility study work on delivering community energy projects for the Marketplace. Supported by \u00a310k from NECA's Energy Accelerator grant, we produced a methodology for validating the carbon savings and social value impact of community projects. This work validated and prepped 5 local community energy projects for upload onto the marketplace. We will now share our findings with all regional authorities. This will unlock investment in the North East; increase the number of community projects delivered and improvement in recording social value.\u00a0 \\n",
