        "sector": "Agriculture, Forestry and Land Use: Green space and/ or biodiversity preservation and expansion",
        "description": "The Woodland Creation Accelerator Fund supports North Yorkshire Council to accelerate the delivery of tree planting and woodland creation commitments. Funding will provide additional officer and consultancy resources to help develop an overall tree planting strategy for North Yorkshire, to identify strategic opportunities and then develop specific projects to submit for grant funding to White Rose Forest partnership and other grant funding routes.\\n\\nhttps://www.gov.uk/guidance/woodland-creation-accelerator-fund-wcaf",
