        "impacts": "Impacts on vulnerable habitats due to greater incidence of drought, drier conditions, increase in dry fuel load/vegetation cover. \\n\\nIncreased levels of fire risk on vulnerable and high-risk habitat areas and nature reserves. \\n\\nRisk of impacts on farm land, rural businesses and properties near to or adjoining high fire risk areas.\\n\\nRisk of harm, injury or death to front line staff, fire crews and the public from wild-fires that get out of control.",
